Privacy Policy
1. Information Collection
The tool does not collect personal information by default.
If registration is required, basic details like your email or username may be collected for licensing purposes.
2. Use of Information
Any collected information is used solely to verify your license and provide updates if necessary.
Your data will not be sold or shared with third parties.
3. Data Security
Reasonable measures are in place to protect your data.
Users are responsible for maintaining the security of their own systems.
4. User Rights
You may request deletion of your data by contacting the developer.
You have the right to know what information is stored about you.
5. Updates to Privacy Policy
Changes to the policy will be communicated through the official registration site or email.
